sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User Browser
    participant Router as OpenShift Router<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Service as odh-dashboard Service<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant OAuth as OAuth Proxy<br/>8443/TCP
    participant OSAuth as OpenShift OAuth<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Backend as Backend (Fastify)<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Pipeline as Data Science Pipelines<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant MR as Model Registry<br/>8080/TCP HTTP/HTTPS
    participant TrustyAI as TrustyAI Service<br/>8080/TCP HTTP/HTTPS
    participant Prometheus as Thanos Querier<br/>9091/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+

    Note over User,Prometheus: Flow 1: User Access Dashboard

    User->>Router: GET / <br/>HTTPS/443
    Router->>Service: Forward<br/>TLS Reencrypt
    Service->>OAuth: Request
    OAuth->>OSAuth: Authenticate<br/>OAuth Client Secret
    OSAuth-->>OAuth: OAuth Token
    OAuth->>Backend: Forward Request<br/>HTTP/8080<br/>Bearer Token
    Backend-->>OAuth: Dashboard HTML
    OAuth-->>Service: Response
    Service-->>Router: Response
    Router-->>User: Dashboard UI

    Note over User,Prometheus: Flow 2: Dashboard to Kubernetes API

    User->>Service: API Request<br/>HTTPS/8443<br/>Bearer Token
    Service->>OAuth: Validate
    OAuth->>Backend: Forward<br/>HTTP/8080
    Backend->>K8sAPI: REST API Call<br/>HTTPS/6443<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI-->>Backend: K8s Resource Data
    Backend-->>OAuth: JSON Response
    OAuth-->>Service: Response
    Service-->>User: API Response

    Note over User,Prometheus: Flow 3: Dashboard to Data Science Pipelines

    User->>Service: /api/service/pipelines/:namespace/:name/*<br/>HTTPS/8443<br/>Bearer Token
    Service->>OAuth: Validate
    OAuth->>Backend: Proxy Request<br/>HTTP/8080
    Backend->>Pipeline: Proxy to Pipeline API<br/>HTTPS/8443<br/>Bearer Token (User passthrough)
    Pipeline-->>Backend: Pipeline Data
    Backend-->>OAuth: Response
    OAuth-->>Service: Response
    Service-->>User: Pipeline Response

    Note over User,Prometheus: Flow 4: Dashboard to Model Registry

    User->>Service: /api/service/modelregistry/:namespace/:name/*<br/>HTTPS/8443<br/>Bearer Token
    Service->>OAuth: Validate
    OAuth->>Backend: Proxy Request<br/>HTTP/8080
    Backend->>MR: Proxy to MR API<br/>HTTP/HTTPS 8080<br/>Bearer Token (User passthrough)
    MR-->>Backend: Model Metadata
    Backend-->>OAuth: Response
    OAuth-->>Service: Response
    Service-->>User: Model Registry Response

    Note over User,Prometheus: Flow 5: Dashboard to TrustyAI

    User->>Service: /api/service/trustyai/:namespace/:name/*<br/>HTTPS/8443<br/>Bearer Token
    Service->>OAuth: Validate
    OAuth->>Backend: Proxy Request<br/>HTTP/8080
    Backend->>TrustyAI: Proxy to TrustyAI API<br/>HTTP/HTTPS 8080<br/>Bearer Token (User passthrough)
    TrustyAI-->>Backend: Bias Metrics
    Backend-->>OAuth: Response
    OAuth-->>Service: Response
    Service-->>User: TrustyAI Response

    Note over User,Prometheus: Flow 6: Dashboard to Prometheus

    Backend->>Prometheus: Query Metrics<br/>HTTPS/9091<br/>Bearer Token (ServiceAccount)
    Prometheus-->>Backend: Metrics Data
